CatDescriptText: Related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 13, 1959, pg. A13, reads: "Gloria Grate...smartly attired"
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Gloria Golden Grate wearing floral dress with puffed sleeves, light colored coat, and light colored gloves, holding sides of skirt, posing in her home in preparation for the D.I.'s "Atlantic City U.S.A" revue in the Press Room of the Hotel Sherwyn
